        <div xml:id="TK1127">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>kaṇṇuḷḷār kāta lavarākak kaṇṇum </l>
<l>meḻutēṅ karappāk kaṟintu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>As my lover abides in my eyes, I will not even paint them, for he would (then) have to conceal himself.</l>
